  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q1_IS_HH_HEAD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>1. Before we begin, to confirm, are you the household head?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Bago kita mag-poon, para makumpirma: ika ba an pasyente?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sa dili pa kita magsugod, aron makompirma, ikaw ba ang punoan sa panimalay?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa wala pa ta magsugod, ikaw ba ang ulo sa panimalay?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ugsa kita magtikang, para la makasiguro, ikaw ba an ulo han panimalay?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.RESPONDENT_NAME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>Name: (Last Name, First Name, MI, Extension)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ngaran: (Apelyido, Ngaran, MI, Extension)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Name: (Last Name, First Name, MI, Extension)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ngalan: (Apelyido, Pangalan, MI, Extension)</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano it imo ngaran? (Apelyido, Syahan nga ngaran, Butnga, Dugang ha ngaran )</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_BIRTH_MONTH
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>2. In what month were you born?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa nga buwan ug tuig ka gipanganak?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano nga bulan ngan tuig ka natawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_BIRTH_YEAR
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsang bulana ug tuiga ka gipanganak?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>2. In what year were you born?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano nga bulan ngan tuig ka natawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q2_1_AGE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2.1 Just to confirm, how old are you as of your last birthday (in years)?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pira an edad mo base sa huring kaarawan mo? (sa taon)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pila na ang imong edad base sa imong pinakaulahi nga birthday (sa tuig)?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Para ma-confirm lang, pila na imong edad base sa imong miaging birthday (sa tuig)?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Para la makumpirma, pira na an imo edad tikang han imo urhi nga kaadlawan (ha mga tuig)?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q3_SEX
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>3. What is your sex at birth?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ano an saimong kasarian kan ika pinangaki?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa ang imong sekso sa pagkatawo?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang imong sex sa pagkahimugso?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an imo sekso han imo pagkatawo?</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q4_LGBTQIA
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>4. Are you part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if you are not comfortable answering.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Parte ka ba kan LGBTQIA+ na komunidad? (hal. bakla, tomboy, bi, buda maski ano pa)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Kabahin ba ka sa LGBTQIA+ nga komunidad? (pananglitan: gay, lesbian, bisexual, ug uban pa). Okay ra kung dili ka komportable nga motubag.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Miyembro ba ka sa LGBTQIA+ community? (pananglitan: bayot, tomboy, bisexual, ug uban pa). Okay ra kung dili ka komportable motubag.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kaapi ka ba han komunidad han LGBTQIA+? (pananglitan, bayot, tomboy, biseksuwal, ngan iba pa). Waray problema kun dire ka komportable bumaton</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q5_GROUP
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>5. Which group do you identify with? It is fine if you are not comfortable answering.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Sain na grupo ika?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sa unsang grupo nimo giila imong kaugalingon? Okay ra kung dili ka komportable nga motubag.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsang grupo ka kabahin? Okay ra kung dili ka komportable motubag.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Hain nga grupo an imo ginkikilala? Waray problema kun dire ka komportable bumaton</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q5_GROUP_OTHER_TXT
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>5. Group — Other (specify) text</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>5. Group — Other (specify) text</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>5. Group — Other (specify) text</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>5. Group — Other (specify) text</p>
          WAR: |
