  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q71_GAMOT_UNDERSTAND_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>71. What is your understanding of the GAMOT Package? — Ensures continuous availability of essential medicines</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Sinisiguro an padagos na availability kan essential medicines</p>
          BIS: |
