  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q75_BRAND_GEN_KNOWS
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>75. Do you know the difference between a 'branded' and a 'generic' medicine?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Aram mo ba an pagkakaiba kan "branded asin "generic" na bulong?</p>
