  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q102_VISIT_REASON_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>102. What best describes why you/your household member will visit a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)? — For a general check-up</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Para sa general check-up</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Para sa general check-up</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Para sa general check-up</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>102. What best describes why you/your household member will visit a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)? — For a general check-up</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q102_VISIT_REASON_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>102. What best describes why you/your household member will visit a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)? — To get a health certificate/administrative reason</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Para makakuha health certificate / administrative reason</p>
          BIS: |
