          WAR: |
            <p>Para makakuha hin sertipiko ha panlawas/rason han pagdumara</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q102_VISIT_REASON_O06
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>102. What best describes why you/your household member will visit a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)? — For immunizations/vaccinations</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Para sa immunizations / vaccinations</p>
