  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q102_VISIT_REASON_O07
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>102. What best describes why you/your household member will visit a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)? — My doctor transferred to this health facility</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An sako na doctor ay digdi tiglipat sa pasilidad na ini</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang akong doktor nibalhin niining health facility</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nabalhin sa kini nga pasilidad sa panglawas ang akong doktor</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An akon doktor nagbalhin hini nga pasilidad panlawas</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q102_VISIT_REASON_O08
    conditions:
