  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q128_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>128. What is your understanding about NBB? — Patient does not pay any hospital bill</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An pasyente dai na nagbabayad nin maski anong hospital bill</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pasyente dili mobayad bisan unsang bayronon sa ospital</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang pasyente dili na magbayad sa bayronon sa ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An pasyente waray magbayad hin bisan ano nga baraydan ha ospital</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q128_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>128. What is your understanding about NBB? — Bills are settled between the hospital and PhilHealth</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Mabayad kaan an ospital asin PhilHealth</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang mga bayronon gisettle tali sa ospital ug PhilHealth</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang bayronon gihusay tali sa ospital ug PhilHealth</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Gin-aareglo an mga baraydan han PhilheHealth ha ospital</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q128_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>128. What is your understanding about NBB? — PhilHealth will cover cost of treatment</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An Philhealth iccover gabos an treatment</p>
          BIS: |
