  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q128_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>128. What is your understanding about NBB? — Patients should not be charged extra fees</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Dai dapat singilon nin dagdag na bayadan an pasyente</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dili dapat singlan og dugang bayad ang mga pasyente</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang mga pasyente dili angay pangayoan og dugang bayad</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An mga pasyente diri angay sukton hin dugang nga bayad</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q128_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>128. What is your understanding about NBB? — Medicine and service are already included</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kabilang na an mga gamot asin serbisyo</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Apil na ang tambal ug serbisyo</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Apil na ang tambal ug serbisyo</p>
          WAR: |
