          WAR: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Laboratory tests / diagnostics</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q196_FOREGONE_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Hospital admission / inpatient care</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Hospital admission / inpatient care</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pagpa-admit sa ospital / inpatient care</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Pagpa-admit sa ospital / inpatient care</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Hospital admission / inpatient care</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q196_FOREGONE_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Preventive care (e.g., vaccinations, check-ups)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Preventive care (e.g., vaccinations, check-ups)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Preventive care (pananglitan: bakuna, check-up)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Preventive care (pananglitan, pagpabakuna, check-up)</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Preventive care (e.g., vaccinations, check-ups)</p>
  - name: HOUSEHOLDSURVEY_DICT.Q196_FOREGONE_O06
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Dental care</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Dental care</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dental care</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dental care</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — Dental care</p>
