    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>196. If your household chooses not to spend on health care for financial reasons, what kind of care do you usually forego? — We do not forego care</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Dai man kami kaan</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Wala kami naglikay o nagpahunong sa pag-atiman</p>
          CEB: |
